data.description:
BRAND NEW Columbia River Collection Marlette Manufactured Home 2022

This Clayton Built home has vaulted ceilings with an open concept kitchen, dining and living room area with a bright modern kitchen island and tons of cupboard storage space. (Brand new kitchen appliances included).  Dining room includes a sliding glass door overlooking back yard.  Private master suite and bath with dual sinks, large walk-in shower and extra large walk-in closet. Split bedroom floor plan with spacious secondary bedrooms and easy access to guest bathroom. Large hallway pantry/linen closet. This home is known and recognized for its large, well equipped, multi-purpose laundry room/mud utility room that you will LOVE!!! 

This beautiful home is located on a big quarter acre corner lot in a nice, quiet neighborhood in the city of Craigmont and has plenty of room to add a garage/shop off of the mud room and a patio/deck out back off of the sliding glass door.  There is ample parking for RV in driveway.  The lot is landscape ready.
